data.name: grdOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,MAX(A.BUNHO) BUNHO ,MAX(A.ORDER_DATE) ORDER_DATE ,MAX(A.RESIDENT) DOCTOR ,MAX(C.DOCTOR_NAME) DOCTOR_NAME ,MAX(A.GWA) GWA ,MAX(B.BUSEO_NAME) BUSEO_NAME ,MAX(D.ORDER_REMARK) ORDER_REMARK ,MAX(D.DRG_REMARK) DRG_REMARK ,MAX(A.MAGAM_GUBUN) MAGAM_GUBUN ,MAX(A.BUNRYU1) BUNRYU1 FROM DRG9040 D ,BAS0270 C ,VW_GWA_NAME B ,DRG3010 A WHERE A.JUBSU_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.CHULGO_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS2003 IS NULL AND B.BUSEO_CODE (+)= A.GWA AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.DOCTOR (+)= A.RESIDENT AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND D.IN_OUT_GUBUN (+)= 'I' AND D.JUBSU_DATE (+)= A.JUBSU_DATE AND D.DRG_BUNHO (+)= A.DRG_BUNHO AND D.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE GROUP BY A.BUNHO, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.JUBSU_DATE ORDER BY 1 DESC, 1
